{"type":"message","id":"8720662b","parentId":"eb241f80","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:28:01.733Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-09 22:28:00 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9 [msg:om_x100b524f3839b0acb3d21e6fed4af2f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b524f3839b0acb3d21e6fed4af2f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-09 22:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_b3b3dc776df60982741679029db666e9\"\n}\n```\n\n深度调研市面最热的AI开发工具，并从多维度分析功能特点，具备的优劣势，并给出支持的套餐价格用量，每个开发工具为一个章节，调研不少于5个开发工具，文档保存到知识库https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg文档下"}],"timestamp":1775744881730}}
{"type":"message","id":"da1c1dc2","parentId":"8720662b","timestamp":"2026-04-09T14:28:10.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我深度调研市面上最热的AI开发工具，需要：\n1. 调研不少于5个AI开发工具\n2. 多维度分析功能特点、优劣势\n3. 给出支持的套餐价格用量\n4. 每个工具为一个章节\n5. 保存到指定的飞书知识库文档\n\n首先我需要：\n1. 获取目标知识库的信息\n2. 搜索市面上的AI开发工具\n3. 整理信息并创建文档\n\n让我先获取知识库节点信息，然后开始搜索AI开发工具。","thinkingSignature":"3fc15ac3088f085264a2869d2bfaed696e1460be2b467f71928860f995c106c5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dgg7ok901ren_1","name":"feishu_wiki_space_node","arguments":{"action":"get","token":"JqLawtcbHiYqrskD6EBc2ZmvnXg"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dgg7ok901ren_2","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"AI开发工具 2024 2025 最热 Cursor Copilot Claude Windsurf 全面对比","count":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":149,"output":215,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":37364,"totalTokens":37728,"cost":{"input":0.00008939999999999999,"output":0.000516,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0140115,"total":0.0146169}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775744881731}}
